cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the segmentation of breast masses from mammograms using deep learning techniques. The use of structured support vector machine (SSVM) also suggests that it may belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves the analysis of running time, which could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the use of deep learning techniques could also suggest that it belongs to the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
